Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:35.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}真理与我们共存
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:38.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}无尽的空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:41.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}侵蚀你的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:47.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}因为你从未遭受痛苦与悲伤
